libtegaki-gtk
=============

This package contains reusable user interface components (aka widgets) for
handwriting recognition.

Requirements
------------

Python       2.4    http://www.python.org
pygtk        2.10   http://www.pygtk.org
tegaki

Install
-------

Add the following to your ~/.bashrc file.

tegakiroot=/path/to/hwr/

export PYTHONPATH=$tegakiroot/libtegaki:$tegakiroot/libtegaki-gtk

